1
00:00:38,520 --> 00:00:39,280
I'm telling you

2
00:00:39,880 --> 00:00:41,240
A smart man knows when to yield

3
00:00:41,679 --> 00:00:43,359
Anything the Sheng family wants

4
00:00:44,000 --> 00:00:45,280
No one dares to take it

5
00:00:47,159 --> 00:00:48,200
Sign the contract

6
00:00:48,520 --> 00:00:49,840
Or get ready to go bankrupt

7
00:00:50,039 --> 00:00:50,560
Understood?

8
00:00:51,840 --> 00:00:53,039
I told you

9
00:00:53,200 --> 00:00:54,359
No other demands

10
00:00:54,759 --> 00:00:57,039
Just keep all the factory workers

11
00:00:57,039 --> 00:00:58,399
Then I'll sign the contract

12
00:00:58,600 --> 00:01:00,119
Are you kidding me?

13
00:01:00,719 --> 00:01:02,799
I run a factory to make money

14
00:01:03,359 --> 00:01:05,120
And you dump all this dead weight on me

15
00:01:05,280 --> 00:01:06,560
How am I supposed to profit?

16
00:01:08,799 --> 00:01:10,000
I'll carry this dead weight

17
00:01:15,200 --> 00:01:16,799
Lisa already pulled her investment

18
00:01:17,000 --> 00:01:17,920
With what, exactly?

19
00:01:18,159 --> 00:01:18,920
I still have the Long family

20
00:01:22,159 --> 00:01:24,040
Director Lu, if you sign with the Long family

21
00:01:24,319 --> 00:01:25,280
we guarantee that while keeping

22
00:01:25,280 --> 00:01:27,000
all the workers in their jobs,

23
00:01:27,239 --> 00:01:28,640
we'll add extra medical subsidies

24
00:01:32,640 --> 00:01:33,599
That's great!

25
00:01:33,879 --> 00:01:35,040
When do we sign?

26
00:01:35,400 --> 00:01:37,560
Don't be so quick to decide

27
00:01:42,799 --> 00:01:43,200
Hello?

28
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:44,480
What?

29
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:46,040
Shanshan is missing

30
00:01:46,599 --> 00:01:47,319
Director Lu

31
00:01:48,120 --> 00:01:50,120
If you sign with Prosperity Group

32
00:01:50,280 --> 00:01:51,040
I guarantee you

33
00:01:51,400 --> 00:01:53,319
your daughter will definitely

34
00:01:53,560 --> 00:01:55,120
make it home safe and sound

35
00:01:55,680 --> 00:01:56,959
Sheng Yuanzhou

36
00:01:57,359 --> 00:01:59,079
You're breaking the law

37
00:01:59,319 --> 00:02:00,439
What did you do to my daughter?

38
00:02:00,599 --> 00:02:02,200
I just took her out to have some fun

39
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:03,640
Why are you freaking out?

40
00:02:03,640 --> 00:02:04,439
You scared me to death

41
00:02:06,359 --> 00:02:07,760
Fine, fine, I'll sign the contract

42
00:02:08,039 --> 00:02:08,879
I'll sign it now

43
00:02:09,080 --> 00:02:09,520
Director Lu

44
00:02:10,199 --> 00:02:10,719
You can't sign it

45
00:02:11,039 --> 00:02:12,520
If you sign, you'll fall right into his trap

46
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:14,560
But my daughter is in their hands!

47
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:16,520
Give me some time

48
00:02:16,879 --> 00:02:18,120
I guarantee she'll be safe

49
00:02:18,599 --> 00:02:19,439
Director Lu

50
00:02:21,479 --> 00:02:23,280
My patience has its limits

51
00:02:23,840 --> 00:02:24,360
How about this:

52
00:02:25,080 --> 00:02:26,759
I'll give you the duration of one game

53
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:28,159
After the game ends,

54
00:02:28,719 --> 00:02:31,240
whether your daughter makes it home safely,

55
00:02:32,479 --> 00:02:33,400
I can't guarantee

56
00:02:34,520 --> 00:02:35,280
Think it over carefully

57
00:02:36,080 --> 00:02:36,680
I'm not leaving yet

58
00:02:38,800 --> 00:02:39,479
Trust me

59
00:02:43,479 --> 00:02:44,719
Team fight, team fight, team fight!

60
00:02:44,719 --> 00:02:45,560
Go in, get him!

61
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:47,199
Get him!

62
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:48,400
Attack!

63
00:02:51,080 --> 00:02:51,719
Hurry up!

64
00:02:53,960 --> 00:02:54,439
Trash!

65
00:02:57,080 --> 00:02:57,960
I'm dead!

66
00:02:58,599 --> 00:02:59,599
Well, Director?

67
00:03:00,199 --> 00:03:01,159
Have you thought it through?

68
00:03:01,159 --> 00:03:02,319
Are you signing or not?

69
00:03:05,039 --> 00:03:05,800
I'll sign now

70
00:03:06,879 --> 00:03:07,520
Director Lu

71
00:03:07,919 --> 00:03:09,759
But that's my daughter's life!

72
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:13,960
Hello? How did it go?

73
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:15,280
She's been rescued safely

74
00:03:15,560 --> 00:03:16,479
Have his daughter answer the phone

75
00:03:21,520 --> 00:03:21,919
Hello?

76
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:23,000
Dad

77
00:03:24,719 --> 00:03:25,319
Shanshan

78
00:03:26,719 --> 00:03:27,879
Are you okay?

79
00:03:28,080 --> 00:03:29,639
Dad, I'm fine

80
00:03:29,879 --> 00:03:31,960
A big brother chased all the bad guys away

81
00:03:32,719 --> 00:03:33,680
Good, good

82
00:03:34,560 --> 00:03:35,360
I'm glad you're okay

83
00:03:35,599 --> 00:03:36,439
I'm glad you're okay

84
00:03:36,919 --> 00:03:39,240
I'll definitely have someone escort your daughter home safely

85
00:03:39,960 --> 00:03:40,639
Thank you

86
00:03:41,360 --> 00:03:42,479
Not bad, Zhang Xiaobei

87
00:03:44,240 --> 00:03:44,960
Finding someone

88
00:03:44,960 --> 00:03:46,520
is a piece of cake for the Long family

89
00:03:47,280 --> 00:03:47,919
Sheng Yuanzhou

90
00:03:49,039 --> 00:03:50,400
Don't think you're the only capable one

91
00:03:50,680 --> 00:03:51,599
Just you wait and see

92
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:59,080
Trying to poke the bear, huh?

93
00:03:59,599 --> 00:04:00,840
Truth is, this Sheng Yuanzhou

94
00:04:00,840 --> 00:04:02,199
doesn't have much ability on his own

95
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:03,919
Once he leaves the Long family

96
00:04:04,439 --> 00:04:05,479
he's nothing but a worm

97
00:04:06,280 --> 00:04:07,120
What do you have in mind?

98
00:04:09,680 --> 00:04:10,560
I heard

99
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:12,240
in a few days

100
00:04:13,000 --> 00:04:14,400
it's Master Long's birthday

101
00:04:15,000 --> 00:04:15,960
We must at least

102
00:04:16,079 --> 00:04:17,160
prepare a generous gift

103
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:26,759
You two, listen up

104
00:04:27,399 --> 00:04:29,519
For my 80th birthday in a few days,

105
00:04:30,279 --> 00:04:32,439
I plan to announce the Long family heir

106
00:04:34,560 --> 00:04:37,040
As for which of you will lead the family,

107
00:04:37,319 --> 00:04:38,120
I've thought it through

108
00:04:38,519 --> 00:04:40,480
We'll let the long-lost Long Family Inkstone decide

109
00:04:41,160 --> 00:04:42,399
On my birthday

110
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:45,519
whoever presents the Long Family Inkstone

111
00:04:45,759 --> 00:04:47,160
will be the Long family heir

112
00:04:48,120 --> 00:04:48,920
His last name isn't even Long

113
00:04:49,160 --> 00:04:49,959
What right does he have?

114
00:04:52,560 --> 00:04:54,199
Xiaobei is my last disciple

115
00:04:54,560 --> 00:04:56,319
If I say he's qualified, he's qualified

116
00:04:56,959 --> 00:04:57,600
End of discussion

117
00:05:13,399 --> 00:05:14,000
You wanted to see me?

118
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:15,639
I just acquired a new treasure

119
00:05:15,639 --> 00:05:16,839
I want you to appraise it for me

120
00:05:17,439 --> 00:05:18,519
Come early to Latent Dragon Pavilion tomorrow

121
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:26,000
This Long Family Inkstone

122
00:05:26,399 --> 00:05:27,439
Where did you get it?

123
00:05:28,240 --> 00:05:29,279
That's none of your business

124
00:05:29,600 --> 00:05:30,800
As for me

125
00:05:31,279 --> 00:05:32,399
I'm not interested in antiques

126
00:05:33,199 --> 00:05:34,560
If you like it

127
00:05:35,160 --> 00:05:35,959
it's yours

128
00:05:38,480 --> 00:05:39,560
Out of the blue,

129
00:05:40,839 --> 00:05:41,920
why are you helping me?

130
00:05:42,600 --> 00:05:43,720
As for me,

131
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:45,040
my business relies entirely on connections

132
00:05:45,639 --> 00:05:48,000
If I can build ties with the future head of the Long family,

133
00:05:48,759 --> 00:05:50,560
isn't that a great deal?

134
00:05:56,160 --> 00:05:57,639
I've already handled it

135
00:05:57,920 --> 00:05:58,360
Got it

136
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:05,439
Master Long, may your fortune be as boundless as the sea,

137
00:06:05,680 --> 00:06:06,360
and your life as long as the mountains

138
00:06:06,759 --> 00:06:07,319
Please take a look

139
00:06:07,959 --> 00:06:08,639
Good

140
00:06:16,240 --> 00:06:18,600
It really is the long-lost Long Family Inkstone

141
00:06:21,199 --> 00:06:21,680
Excellent

142
00:06:27,480 --> 00:06:28,759
I now declare

143
00:06:29,160 --> 00:06:31,079
the future head of the Long family is...

144
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:34,839
Master Long

145
00:06:35,560 --> 00:06:35,839
Master Long!

146
00:06:36,759 --> 00:06:37,439
Master Long, what's wrong?

147
00:06:38,040 --> 00:06:39,279
Master Long! Master Long!

148
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:41,439
This...

149
00:06:42,240 --> 00:06:44,560
The Long Family Inkstone is poisoned!

150
00:06:45,439 --> 00:06:46,000
Guards!

151
00:06:46,279 --> 00:06:47,680
Arrest Long Yi! He poisoned it!

152
00:06:49,399 --> 00:06:50,759
It wasn't me, Master Long!

153
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:51,839
Master Long!

154
00:06:52,439 --> 00:06:54,720
Zhang Xiaobei, you set me up!

155
00:07:00,319 --> 00:07:01,279
Sheng Yuanzhou!

156
00:07:02,120 --> 00:07:04,600
I knew you were up to no good

157
00:07:05,319 --> 00:07:06,040
But...

158
00:07:06,800 --> 00:07:07,720
this is perfect

159
00:07:08,959 --> 00:07:09,680
This is the Long Family Inkstone

160
00:07:15,040 --> 00:07:15,560
Don't you dare...

161
00:07:16,319 --> 00:07:17,560
Being able to receive the Long family's protection,

162
00:07:17,560 --> 00:07:18,560
I'm already very grateful

163
00:07:18,879 --> 00:07:19,879
I wouldn't dare have improper ambitions

164
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:24,199
Wise choice

165
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:28,360
Let go of me!

166
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:33,720
If you're willing to leave the Long family on your own,

167
00:07:34,480 --> 00:07:35,399
what happened today,

168
00:07:35,720 --> 00:07:36,720
I'll let slide

169
00:07:37,240 --> 00:07:39,199
Tell everyone Master Long isn't feeling well,

170
00:07:39,199 --> 00:07:39,959
and had a stroke

171
00:07:40,879 --> 00:07:41,759
Otherwise...

172
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:44,600
I'll have you locked up right now

173
00:07:44,600 --> 00:07:45,439
Zhang Xiaobei!

174
00:07:46,360 --> 00:07:47,560
Master Long treated you well!

175
00:07:48,079 --> 00:07:48,800
Why would you...?

176
00:07:49,360 --> 00:07:50,000
Why?!

177
00:07:50,879 --> 00:07:51,680
Let go of me!

178
00:07:52,959 --> 00:07:54,439
Expel Long Yi from the Long family!

179
00:07:55,319 --> 00:07:57,319
Zhang Xiaobei, you heartless bastard!

180
00:07:57,839 --> 00:07:59,079
This won't end well for you!

181
00:07:59,720 --> 00:08:00,399
Zhang Xiaobei!

182
00:08:00,759 --> 00:08:01,519
Let go of me!

183
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:09,639
Thanks for the gift

184
00:08:11,600 --> 00:08:12,879
I really like it

185
00:08:21,079 --> 00:08:22,000
I didn't expect

186
00:08:22,680 --> 00:08:24,040
him to actually have some brains

187
00:08:25,560 --> 00:08:26,959
Mr. Sheng, someone is here to see you

188
00:08:36,039 --> 00:08:38,159
I knew you'd agree to cooperate with me

189
00:08:42,600 --> 00:08:43,399
Long Yi brought this

190
00:08:43,399 --> 00:08:45,200
Baochi Automobile Factory's core tech files

191
00:08:45,960 --> 00:08:46,799
Once the funding is in place,

192
00:08:47,399 --> 00:08:48,559
we can start production anytime

193
00:08:49,879 --> 00:08:51,679
We can beat them to the product launch

194
00:08:52,320 --> 00:08:53,519
and seize the market first

195
00:08:54,080 --> 00:08:54,879
Great

196
00:08:55,519 --> 00:08:56,279
Nice work

197
00:08:57,600 --> 00:08:58,519
We'll do it your way

198
00:09:07,879 --> 00:09:09,720
I heard Prosperity Group

199
00:09:09,720 --> 00:09:11,399
is using the files Long Yi gave them

200
00:09:11,399 --> 00:09:12,759
to push ahead with development and production

201
00:09:13,080 --> 00:09:14,960
They'll definitely launch before us

202
00:09:16,320 --> 00:09:17,519
We just need to focus on ourselves

203
00:09:18,279 --> 00:09:19,200
No need to worry too much about them

204
00:09:19,639 --> 00:09:20,759
Aren't you worried?

205
00:09:22,960 --> 00:09:25,519
Or did you never intend to save our factory at all?

206
00:09:35,559 --> 00:09:37,159
We put in so much money up front,

207
00:09:37,399 --> 00:09:39,279
and now you're saying it can't be developed?

208
00:09:39,679 --> 00:09:41,159
Everything was going smoothly at first

209
00:09:41,679 --> 00:09:43,200
But whenever it hits a critical moment, it always...

210
00:09:44,720 --> 00:09:45,120
Come in

211
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:48,240
Chairman, take a look at this

212
00:09:49,279 --> 00:09:50,039
Longbao Motors

213
00:09:50,360 --> 00:09:51,759
will mark the start of the Long family's transformation

214
00:09:52,039 --> 00:09:53,200
We'll combine AI technology

215
00:09:53,440 --> 00:09:54,600
with new energy,

216
00:09:54,919 --> 00:09:56,600
committed to driving a new revolution in mobility

217
00:09:56,720 --> 00:09:57,159
Today,

218
00:09:57,960 --> 00:09:59,120
I solemnly declare here that

219
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:00,679
I will lead the Long family

220
00:10:00,919 --> 00:10:02,720
into the automotive industry

221
00:10:06,279 --> 00:10:06,960
Chairman

222
00:10:07,200 --> 00:10:08,480
So are we still launching?

223
00:10:08,559 --> 00:10:09,440
What launch?!

224
00:10:10,840 --> 00:10:11,960
The technology is exactly the same

225
00:10:11,960 --> 00:10:13,159
But our costs are double theirs

226
00:10:13,240 --> 00:10:14,720
Then won't the money we invested up front

227
00:10:14,720 --> 00:10:15,679
go down the drain?

228
00:10:15,679 --> 00:10:16,480
You think I don't know that?

229
00:10:16,879 --> 00:10:17,879
Do I need you to remind me?

230
00:10:20,840 --> 00:10:22,279
If we want to minimize our losses,

231
00:10:23,159 --> 00:10:24,639
we can only count on the government's

232
00:10:24,879 --> 00:10:26,159
newly established development zone

233
00:10:28,080 --> 00:10:28,919
You're right

234
00:10:29,840 --> 00:10:30,399
But...

235
00:10:30,519 --> 00:10:31,919
whether it's East City or West City,

236
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:34,320
they haven't announced it yet

237
00:10:34,919 --> 00:10:37,240
It probably won't be announced until after the land auction

238
00:10:38,919 --> 00:10:40,279
From a transportation standpoint,

239
00:10:41,000 --> 00:10:42,360
I think East City District is most likely

240
00:10:43,279 --> 00:10:45,120
It connects the north and south expressways

241
00:10:45,759 --> 00:10:47,879
And I heard

242
00:10:48,320 --> 00:10:49,919
Sheng Yuanzhou recently

243
00:10:50,639 --> 00:10:51,639
also took people

244
00:10:52,320 --> 00:10:53,480
to scout East City District

245
00:10:54,559 --> 00:10:55,399
So I suspect

246
00:10:55,919 --> 00:10:57,080
they're also eyeing

247
00:10:57,320 --> 00:10:59,480
the government's new development zone

248
00:11:00,159 --> 00:11:01,840
The Long family built its fortune on antiques

249
00:11:02,519 --> 00:11:04,200
They've always had strong ties with the higher-ups

250
00:11:05,799 --> 00:11:07,320
They didn't scout East City

251
00:11:08,159 --> 00:11:09,399
for no reason

252
00:11:15,279 --> 00:11:17,399
Are they trying to take East City?
